import React from 'react'
import Header from '../Component/Header'
import Footer from '../Component/Footer'
import Otherslide from '../Component/Otherslide'
import Contacttop from '../Component/Contact Component/Contacttop'
import Contactdeatils from '../Component/Contact Component/Contactdeatils'
import Contactmap from '../Component/Contact Component/Contactmap'

function Contact() {
    return (
        <>

            <Header />
            <Otherslide />
            <Contacttop />
            <Contactdeatils />
            <Contactmap />
            <Footer />

        </>
    )
}

export default Contact
